{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_184","type":"agent_message","text":"Static provider registration does work in principle, but native-image rejects persisting a BC provider instance unless `org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider` is initialized at build time. I’m validating that combined setup now before I change the repo build for this test project."}}
